The median age was 46.0 years.
For every 100 females there were 266.7 males.
For every 100 females age 18 and over, there were 375.0 males.
There were 30 housing units at an average density of 41.4 per square mile (16.0/km²), of which 6 (46.2%) were owner-occupied, and 7 (53.8%) were occupied by renters.
